&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Physiotherapy Technician&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kingston Hospital NHS Foundation Trust is an acute general hospital serving South West London and Surrey. We have a superb reputation for innovation in the field of healthcare and have recently been awarded an outstanding rating from CQC for caring and leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic Physiotherapy Technician to join the inpatient Physiotherapy team. This role will involve supporting and working as part of the physiotherapy team in promoting mobility, rehabilitation and exercises.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a very friendly, supportive team who encourage innovative and dynamic applicants who have an interest in physiotherapy and a passion for rehabilitation. We actively encourage in-service training and recognise the value of supervision and appraisal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameEmily OrmeJob titleInpatient Team Lead PhysiotherapistEmail addressemilyorme@nhs.netTelephone numberext 2881Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For an informal discussion and/or visit please contact Emily Orme (emilyorme@nhs.net)&lt;/p&gt;
